original_title: Kate Bliss and the Ticker Tape Kid
overview: A turn-of-the-century investigator named Kate Bliss goes to the wide-open spaces of the wild west to capture a gang of outlaws led by a charming "Robin Hood of the plains," leading a band of dispossessed ranchers against a stuffy English land baron who has cheated them out of their property.
title: Kate Bliss and the Ticker Tape Kid
